response.original_title: P Money feat. Whiney - Live at Hospitality Printworks
response.overview: This DJ set was recorded on April 15, 2023, at Printworks London, during Hospitality’s “Closing Chapter” event, marking the end of their long-standing residency at the venue. Performing back-to-back, the duo delivered a continuous mix spanning approximately one hour. While no official tracklist is published, audience uploads refer to signature tracks and unreleased IDs. The performance was filmed and posted by Hospital Records on both YouTube and SoundCloud on January 31, 2024. The set encapsulates the energetic atmosphere of a true club closing night at an iconic venue, blending rapid-fire MC sections by P Money with Whiney’s melodic D&B lines.
response.title: P Money feat. Whiney - Live at Hospitality Printworks
